svg.title: Job Seeker Flows (J1-J9) - Tinder-Style Matching App

g.text: Job Seeker Flows (J1-J9) - Tinder-Style Matching App
Sign up (personal email, LinkedIn, or SSO) → verify
Enter basics (name, location, desired roles, availability)
Add skills, industries, job type, seniority
Optional: portfolio links or short intro video
ATS integration via *Sys2* for pipeline creation
Join company events; RSVP + QR check-in
Access resource hub: resume tips, interview prep, mentors
Receive new match and profile view alerts
Weekly digest of roles matching profile
View pipeline stages mirrored from recruiter system
No reply after X days → reminder or auto-close
